    "long_instructions": "####<i class=\"fa-solid fa-music\"></i> Now you're the songwriter, producer or sound designer!\r\nCreate your own song or music for a story or game! \r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-check\"></i> Make music with **sequenced** code.\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-check\"></i>  Use **functions** to keep organized.\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-check\"></i>  Add **event** triggers to control when sounds play.\r\n\r\n--- \r\nYou can choose a different song any time! \r\n\r\n[<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb-on\"></i> Hint](#clickable=start-over-button)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
